data.description: Stunning Home in a Prime Cul-De-Sac Location with Modern Updates! As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a new front door and an array of fresh updates, including: Brand-new black high-end Anderson windows, freshly painted in a crisp white, creating a bright and airy atmosphere that complements any decor style, New luxury vinyl wide plank flooring spans the living areas, adding a contemporary touch while ensuring durability and easy maintenance. All interior doors have been replaced. The new light fixtures lend a touch of glamour and accentuate the overall aesthetic. In the heart of the home, the updated kitchen proudly displays a new refrigerator and oven. The bathrooms have undergone meticulous remodeling with new vanities mirrors, toilets, flooring and light fixtures. New sub floor under patio door. New shelving system in primary bedroom. The addition of the new pergola offers both shade and charm, creating a perfect setting for outdoor dining or quiet moments spent savoring the tranquility of the surroundings. Situated in a coveted location, it is merely a stone's throw away from a variety of shopping options and an array of restaurants, making it an epicenter of entertainment and convenience. Schedule a tour today and envision your future in this remarkable residence!
